quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  67,27,"Saha shεli bɛ (chɛfurinim’) ni ti nya li (azaaba maa) ka di miri na, ka bɛ saɣim bɛ nina, ka bɛ (Malaaikanima) yεli ba: “Ŋɔ maa n-nyɛ yi ni daa bɔri shεli ni yomyom’ (Dunia puuni) la"
  67,28,"(Yaa nyini Annabi)! Yεlima: “Di ni bɔŋɔ, Naawuni yi ku ma, n-ti pahi ninvuɣu shεba ban pahi n zuɣu, bee ka O zo ti nambɔɣu, tɔ! Ŋuni n-leei yɛn tilgi chεfurinim’ ka chɛ azaaba- kpeeni?”"
  67,29,"Yεlima: “Ŋuna n-nyɛ Nambɔzobo- naa, ka ti ti O yεlimaŋli. Yaha! O zuɣu ka ti dalim, dinzuɣu ni baalim, yi ni ti baŋ ŋun be birginsim din be polo ni.”"
  67,30,"Yεlima: “(Yaa nyini Annabi)! Di ni- bɔŋɔ, yi bi nya kadama yi ko’ shɛli yi ni nyuri yi leei din nyuui, ka ŋuni n-leei yɛn tooi tahi ya ko’ shεli din bilsiri tingbani ni na"
  68,1,"Nuun (N). [Bachi gaŋ ŋɔ maa wuhirimi ni Alkur’aani nyɛla Muɣujizah (lahiʒibsi din ka ŋmali), dama so ʒi di gbinni naɣila Naawuni]. M (Mani Naawuni) Po alkalmi, ni bɛ (Malaaikanim’) ni sabri shɛli"
  68,2,(Yaa nyini Annabi)! A pala yinyaa domin a Duuma (Naawuni) ni ti a yolsigu shεli maa zuɣu
  68,3,Yaha! Achiika! A mali sanyo’ shɛli (laara) din ka ŋmaabu
  68,4,(Yaa nyini Annabi)! Achiika! A nyɛla Ŋun be hali shεŋa din gahim zuɣu
  68,5,"Dinzuɣu ni baalim, a ni ti nya, ka bɛ (Maka chεfurinim’) gba nya"
  68,6,Yi puuni ŋuni n-leei nyɛ yinyaa
  68,7,"Achiika! A Duuma (Naawuni) mi ninvuɣu so ŋun bɔrgi ka chɛ O soli, ka lahi mi ninvuɣu shεba ban dolsi"
  68,8,Dinzuɣu (Yaa nyini Annabi)! Di doli ninvuɣu shεba ban labsiri (Alkur’aani) ʒiri maa
  68,9,"Bɛ (Maka chεfurinim’ maa) di bɔri mi ni a balgi yεla pam n-ti ba, ka bɛ gba balgi yεla n-ti a"
  68,10,"(Yaha! Yaa nyini Annabi)! Di doli ŋun kam pɔri Naawuni yiriŋ, ka nyɛ ŋun filiŋ"
  68,11,"Ŋun zuri niriba nyaaŋa, ka chani ni tuɣuligu"
  68,12,"Ŋun mɔŋdi alheeri, ka kpahiri yεɣira, ka zooi Naawuni taali ni kpɛbu"
  68,13,"Ŋun nyɛ suhukuŋ lana, din nyaaŋa, ka o pa halali bia"
  68,14,"Domin o nyɛ bundana, ka mali bihi zuɣu"
  68,15,"Bɛ yi ti karindi Ti (Tinim’ Naawuni) aayanima n-tiri o, ka o yεli: “Ŋɔ maa nyɛla kurumbuni nima salima.”"